## Troubleshooting Common Issues

### Context Project Not Found
- Use `@projects list` to see available projects
- Check project naming and ensure it's enabled
- Verify `.contexts` folder structure

### Git Updates Failing
- Check internet connection and repository access
- Ensure Git credentials are properly configured
- Use extension's auto-update features instead of manual git commands

### Large File Issues
- Extension automatically handles file size limits
- Binary files are filtered out automatically
- Use .gitignore patterns for Git-based projects

## Remember
The Cursor Contexts extension is designed to make AI interactions more contextual and productive. Always consider how context projects can enhance your responses and suggestions to users. When in doubt, check the `.contexts` folder first!